THE PRIDE OF SEYANG HIGH SCHOOL

4
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:33,510
HIS KNEE IS BUSTED!

5
00:01:33,593 --> 00:01:35,303
HE'S DOOMED!

6
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:45,313
The megaphone.

7
00:01:47,565 --> 00:01:48,775
Jung Yi-hyun!

8
00:01:48,858 --> 00:01:51,611
I know how you feel.
I was in Little League too.

9
00:01:52,111 --> 00:01:55,365
So come down and talk. Come down.

10
00:01:55,448 --> 00:01:57,158
You can just talk from there.

11
00:01:57,784 --> 00:02:00,036
-What did he say?
-I couldn't hear him.

12
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,038
Then give him a megaphone too.

13
00:02:03,289 --> 00:02:06,417
I'll go up there, so wait a bit.

14
00:02:06,501 --> 00:02:08,795
Let's talk when I get up there.

15
00:02:08,878 --> 00:02:10,213
Where are the stairs?

16
00:02:17,178 --> 00:02:18,388
He's just not coming down.

17
00:02:19,097 --> 00:02:20,932
Focus on your books.

18
00:02:22,141 --> 00:02:25,353
If you focus, you can't even hear
a bomb exploding next to you.

19
00:02:25,436 --> 00:02:27,605
But classes are over.
Why aren't we going home?

20
00:02:27,689 --> 00:02:29,232
No one can focus right now anyway.

21
00:02:29,315 --> 00:02:32,443
Do you think Yi-hyun would be
happy if you ran out in a crowd?

22
00:02:33,111 --> 00:02:34,904
He's already mentally unstable.

23
00:02:34,988 --> 00:02:37,490
And if he jumps off impulsively
after seeing you guys,

24
00:02:38,116 --> 00:02:41,411
I'm sure that'll help you focus
when you get home.

25
00:02:42,078 --> 00:02:44,330
So you'll send us home
if he comes down, right?

26
00:02:44,414 --> 00:02:47,167
Yes, I'll send you home right away.

27
00:02:47,250 --> 00:02:48,918
The police are negotiating with him,

28
00:02:49,002 --> 00:02:51,421
so don’t provoke me.
Just lie on your desk and sleep.

29
00:02:52,672 --> 00:02:54,424
You've been a student for a long time.

30
00:02:54,507 --> 00:02:55,925
It must be hard for you too.

31
00:02:56,509 --> 00:02:59,429
-I'm going to the restroom.
-Hey, I told you not to provoke me…

32
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:03,516
Well, let's just keep quiet, please.

33
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,851
Hey, all of you, focus!

34
00:03:04,934 --> 00:03:07,103
Focus on your books.
The bomb is being dropped.

35
00:03:09,606 --> 00:03:14,944
I will make sure
that you're all cured, okay?

36
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:17,906
If that can't be done,
I'll make you a cop at the very least.

37
00:03:17,989 --> 00:03:20,116
So trust me and come down, okay?

38
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:21,868
I don't want to be a cop.

39
00:03:21,951 --> 00:03:23,202
All right!

40
00:03:26,873 --> 00:03:30,084
I'm his friend. I was told to come up
so I can help negotiate with him.

41
00:03:30,168 --> 00:03:33,379
Talk here. I won't go. Talk here, okay?

42
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,423
Calm down first.

43
00:03:36,799 --> 00:03:37,842
Yoon Sae-bom?

44
00:03:38,635 --> 00:03:39,761
Hey!

45
00:03:40,595 --> 00:03:41,846
Hey!

46
00:03:42,555 --> 00:03:44,891
Hey, young lady!

47
00:03:44,974 --> 00:03:46,434
Wait!

48
00:03:46,517 --> 00:03:47,602
Who are you?

49
00:03:48,102 --> 00:03:50,229
-Are you his girlfriend?
-No.

50
00:03:50,313 --> 00:03:52,190
Hey, we can't go home because of you!

51
00:03:52,815 --> 00:03:55,568
Mister, I will persuade him,
so wait there for a moment.

52
00:03:56,069 --> 00:03:58,363
What's wrong with
the students at this school?

53
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,912
Are you upset you can't play baseball?

54
00:04:06,412 --> 00:04:07,789
That's not what it is.

55
00:04:08,748 --> 00:04:10,750
I just came up here
because I was frustrated,

56
00:04:10,833 --> 00:04:13,419
but ambulances and police cars
suddenly arrived.

57
00:04:14,587 --> 00:04:16,214
Which idiot made a report?

58
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:19,884
I'm just waiting to see
how far this will go.

59
00:04:19,968 --> 00:04:21,261
I have nothing to do anyway.

60
00:04:22,053 --> 00:04:24,138
Don't you have anything to do
besides baseball?

61
00:04:24,222 --> 00:04:25,056
I don't.

62
00:04:25,682 --> 00:04:27,183
I did it my entire life.

63
00:04:27,266 --> 00:04:28,768
I was really good at it too.

64
00:04:29,269 --> 00:04:31,896
And I ended up like this.
Would you be okay if you were me?

65
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,232
I did nothing my entire life,
but I was okay.

66
00:04:34,315 --> 00:04:36,693
Hey, doing nothing is way better.

67
00:04:37,193 --> 00:04:38,861
I was hospitalized for a long time.

68
00:04:38,945 --> 00:04:41,489
And you know, it all just becomes
a good memory later on.

69
00:04:42,532 --> 00:04:44,826
I can't play baseball ever again.

70
00:04:44,909 --> 00:04:48,288
My life is over.
I don't know what to do in my life.

71
00:04:52,792 --> 00:04:53,876
What about you, then?

72
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,545
What are you going to do?

73
00:04:56,671 --> 00:04:58,506
I wanted to be a nurse until last week,

74
00:04:58,589 --> 00:05:00,300
but a public official seems nice too.

75
00:05:00,383 --> 00:05:02,844
I would need a monthly paycheck,

76
00:05:02,927 --> 00:05:04,220
but I keep changing my mind.

77
00:05:04,721 --> 00:05:07,974
See? You're feeling unsettled too
for being two years behind.

78
00:05:08,057 --> 00:05:09,267
No.

79
00:05:10,226 --> 00:05:13,563
I'm saying there's no limit
to our futures.

80
00:05:15,732 --> 00:05:18,985
It's okay, so just do it,

81
00:05:19,068 --> 00:05:21,279
and think that it's fine
even if it doesn't work.

82
00:05:38,504 --> 00:05:39,714
Like me.

83
00:06:19,629 --> 00:06:20,797
No, Mister.

84
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:24,550
I planned to make him fall
onto the cushion.

85
00:06:45,488 --> 00:06:47,156
Okay, let's talk when we get there.

86
00:06:47,949 --> 00:06:49,283
-Let go of me!
-Hey!

87
00:06:49,951 --> 00:06:51,077
Jung Yi-hyun!

88
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:54,038
Tell him that you don't want me
to get punished.

89
00:06:54,122 --> 00:06:55,623
He's going to arrest me.

90
00:06:55,706 --> 00:06:56,999
Hey, Yoon Sae-bom.

91
00:07:03,256 --> 00:07:04,757
Do you want to be my girlfriend?

