126
00:10:44,435 --> 00:10:45,895
Yoon Sae-bom!

127
00:10:46,687 --> 00:10:47,897
What are you doing?

128
00:10:49,065 --> 00:10:51,525
They had to make this because of you.

129
00:10:51,609 --> 00:10:54,362
You stabbed his chest directly with it

130
