Excuse me, you have to pay
if you damage the motel's property.

146
00:12:15,568 --> 00:12:16,902
Do you want to get beaten up?

147
00:12:29,999 --> 00:12:33,002
It's hard to endure weather
that's gradually getting hotter,

148
