will get special provisions for that.

236
00:18:41,119 --> 00:18:43,122
Really? What are the conditions?

237
00:18:43,205 --> 00:18:45,749
My wife's dream is to move
into that new apartment.

238
00:18:45,833 --> 00:18:48,001
They give extra points
for long-term service,

239
00:18:48,085 --> 00:18:50,087
family members to provide for,
and newlyweds.

240
00:18:50,170 --> 00:18:53,715
The biggest chunks come from
arrest records and work evaluations.

241
00:18:53,799 --> 00:18:55,968
Once I'm chosen,
I'll get an apartment for sure.

242
00:18:56,051 --> 00:18:57,761
It's like winning the lottery.

243
00:18:57,845 --> 00:19:00,639
Who are we going to arrest? Terrorists?

244
00:19:01,807 --> 00:19:04,309
You never know
what might happen in life, okay?

245
00:19:04,393 --> 00:19:06,979
If I show something today…

246
00:19:07,479 --> 00:19:08,856
What are you going to show?

247
00:19:09,606 --> 00:19:10,774
I'm thinking.

248
00:19:22,327 --> 00:19:24,997
Take it easy with sports.
Don't get injured again.

249
00:19:25,080 --> 00:19:26,164
Okay.

250
00:19:33,088 --> 00:19:34,590
(I AM) THE LIFESAVER

